Palettes are memory in the PPU that you must copy those bytes to.<br /><br /><a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_palettes" class="postlink">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_palettes</a><br /><br />To upload data to the PPU's memory see:<br /><br /><a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_registers" class="postlink">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_registers</a><br /><br />Specifically $2002, $2006, and $2007.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=5165">rainwarrior</a> — Tue May 22, 2012 2:31 pm</p><hr />
